summary: This document details the collection of highly confidential responsive material from digital evidence processed by the FBI's Computer Analysis Response Team (CART) related to the Epstein case. It includes references to child victim and witness identity information, emphasizing the confidentiality and sensitivity of the material, which consists of nude and semi-nude images and videos.

persons.name: Jeffrey Epstein
persons.context: Jeffrey Epstein is identified as the central figure in the child sex trafficking investigation, with the document containing evidence related to his case.

events.title: Collection of Digital Evidence
events.description: Digital evidence, including highly confidential material, was collected by the FBI's CART.

keyFacts: The document contains highly confidential material related to child victims and witnesses.
Nude and semi-nude images and videos were processed from digital evidence.
The material is restricted to individuals with a need-to-know for the associated proceedings.
